cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper deals with analyzing knowledge consistency between pre-trained deep neural networks, which is a core topic in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the disentanglement of feature components, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper proposes a task-agnostic method, which is relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural engineering (cs.NE).
